{"about_the_game":"<u><strong>Enhance your Windows experience with Containers</strong></u><br><br>Containers allows the storage of your files and folders in boxes called <strong>\u201cContainer\u201d</strong>, these boxes can be accessed at any time on your desktop or called thanks to built-in shortcuts or with the help of the <strong>\u201cContainers Tab\u201d</strong> menu.<br><br><strong><u>Containers</u></strong><br>Containers are sticked to your desktop when you don't use them.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989710/extras/Desc1.png?t=1678104038\" /><br><br><strong><u>Mirror Containers</u></strong><br>\u201cMirror\u201d Containers are representations of files and folders in a selected folder on your computer.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989710/extras/Desc3.png?t=1678104038\" /><br><br><strong><u>Container Customization</u></strong><br>Containers can have different colored backgrounds or a background with an image.<br>You can also set the transparency method of your Containers.<br><br>If you are on Windows 11 you can also choose between Containers with rounded or squared edges.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989710/extras/Desc6.png?t=1678104038\" /><br><br><strong><u>Containers Tab Menu</u></strong><br>The Containers Tab menu allows you to call the Container of your choice without leaving the application in the foreground, it works similarly to the Alt-Tab menu in Windows.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989710/extras/Desc2.png?t=1678104038\" /><br><br><strong><u>Closing Containers</u></strong><br>Containers can be independently closed manually or automatically to save space.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989710/extras/Desc4.png?t=1678104038\" /><br><br><strong><u>Sorting Containers content</u></strong><br>You can independently sort the contents of your Containers according to your choice.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989710/extras/Desc5.png?t=1678104038\" /><br><br><strong><u>Container content size</u></strong><br>You can change the size of your Container icons at any time.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989710/extras/Desc6.png?t=1678104038\" /><br><br><strong><u>Shortcuts</u></strong><br>The Containers application has shortcuts to help you manipulate your Containers, each shortcut can be modified and disabled.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Colorful","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1989710/484cf281e03cfb6d5f38ecc77c78e2fbbdbc970d.jpg"},{"name":"1 + 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1989710/7a389ad5ead5cd8b1d17b9e371487037689a9de0.jpg"},{"name":"Containers Tab Menu","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1989710/86e86ffb7c8a778e45e2ad41e02110ac5fdb7fa0.jpg"}],"total":3},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989710/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1678104038","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989710/page.bg.jpg?t=1678104038","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989710/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1678104038","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989710/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1678104038","categories":[{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<u><strong>Enhance your Windows experience with Containers</strong></u><br><br>Containers a